      <title>前财政部长弗里兰加入加拿大总理竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ex-finance-minister-freeland-jumps-into-race-to-lead-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大前财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 于 12 月辞职，结束了贾斯汀·特鲁多的政治生涯，如今她已加入继任总理的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ex-finance-minister-freeland-jumps-into-race-to-lead-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 13:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列安全内阁批准加沙停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/israel-security-cabinet-approves-deal-for-ceasefire-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级安全内阁批准与哈马斯达成停火及人质与囚犯交换协议，为从周日开始至加沙持续 15 个月的战斗暂停数周铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/israel-security-cabinet-approves-deal-for-ceasefire-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 13:07:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临山火威胁，洛杉矶仍加快重建家园</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-17/california-fast-tracks-rebuilding-of-la-homes-despite-fire-danger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些规定已被取消，以鼓励迅速更换被烧毁的房屋。消防专家表示，新建房屋必须能够抵御未来的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-17/california-fast-tracks-rebuilding-of-la-homes-despite-fire-danger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 13:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛承诺应特朗普要求增加国防开支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/lithuania-pledges-to-boost-defense-spending-after-trump-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普敦促欧洲盟友增加军事资金后，立陶宛计划增加国防开支，以阻止来自俄罗斯的潜在威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/lithuania-pledges-to-boost-defense-spending-after-trump-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台后马萨诸塞州考虑实施更严格的庇护规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/massachusetts-weighs-tougher-shelter-rules-as-trump-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马萨诸塞州州长莫拉·希利承诺与州立法机构合作，改革超负荷的紧急避难所系统，该系统每年耗资约 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/massachusetts-weighs-tougher-shelter-rules-as-trump-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:47:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟辩论放弃对华贸易诉讼，令特朗普顾问感到沮丧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/eu-debates-dropping-china-trade-case-frustrating-trump-advisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在讨论是否放弃针对中国涉嫌针对立陶宛采取强制性活动的敏感贸易调查，这一前景让华盛顿的官员感到沮丧，即将上任的特朗普团队认为这是向北京的屈服。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/eu-debates-dropping-china-trade-case-frustrating-trump-advisers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚各州州长有条件支持税收改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/nigeria-state-governors-give-conditional-backing-to-tax-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚各州有权有势的州长们不再反对国家税收改革，但条件是放弃削减企业税和提高增值税的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/nigeria-state-governors-give-conditional-backing-to-tax-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨否认将自身政治生存置于支持乌克兰之上的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/german-chancellor-scholz-denies-prioritizing-relection-over-support-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨反驳了有关他抛弃乌克兰以在下个月提前选举前为落后的社会民主党争取支持的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/german-chancellor-scholz-denies-prioritizing-relection-over-support-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 12:11:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙桑切斯预算谈判受挫 失去加泰罗尼亚盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/spanish-prime-minister-loses-a-catalan-ally-as-party-stops-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯的一位重要盟友表示，这将破坏所有谈判，对正在寻求批准新预算的社会党政府造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/spanish-prime-minister-loses-a-catalan-ally-as-party-stops-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 11:33:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯和伊朗将在特朗普任期前签署伙伴关系协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/russia-and-iran-to-sign-partnership-pact-ahead-of-new-trump-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周五与伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安举行峰会，开始签署一项新协议，两国正为美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/russia-and-iran-to-sign-partnership-pact-ahead-of-new-trump-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 06:36:26 GMT</pubDate>
